RH-Author: Peter Xu <peterx@redhat.com>
RH-MergeRequest: 150: migration: Fix multifd crash on channel disorders
RH-Bugzilla: 2169732
RH-Acked-by: quintela1 <quintela@redhat.com>
RH-Acked-by: Leonardo Br√°s <leobras@redhat.com>
